2018.</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tc.columbia.edu/faculty/hl361/faculty-profile/files/Henry-Levin-CV.pdf\">Curriculum vitae of Henry Levin from the website of Columbia University. Retrieved March 31st, 2018.</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Henry_Levin_(economist)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tc.columbia.edu/faculty/hl361/\">Webpage of Henry Levin on the website of Teacher's College</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1242\nCached time: 20180910020212\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.108 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 274/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 4075/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 97/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 3018/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 1/400\nLua time usage: 0.028/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.22 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   84.165      1 -total\n 52.56%   44.236      1 Template:Primary_sources\n 34.13%   28.725      1 Template:Ambox\n 26.61%   22.393      1 Template:Authority_control\n 15.51%   13.054      1 Template:Reflist\n  4.04%    3.402      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:56996850-0!cano